    <sect3 role="package">
      <title>Introduction to html5lib Module</title>

      <para>
        <application>html5lib</application> provides a pure-python library for
        parsing HTML. It is designed to conform to the WHATWG HTML
        specification.
      </para>

      &lfs130_checked;

